Title: Adding Audio Visualization to a React App With Web Audio API
Description: In this post, we will build a simple React app that shows how to use the Web Audio API to extract audio data and display some visuals on the screen.

Title: How to Handle Numbers Represented as Strings in the Input to a .NET AWS Lambda Function | no dogma blog
Description: If you invoke a Lambda function with a number represented as a string, and you are using the DefaultLambdaJsonSerializer it will fail. This post shows how to get around that problem in two ways.
